Program: Discovery
Title: Hope for a Malaria vaccine
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwy4
Last Broadcast Date: 04 August 1997
A new lead in the hunt for a malaria vaccine. Also in the programme, a dive into Roman history deep under the ocean, how life in the womb programs the fight against disease and a mission to Mars. Presenter: Graeme Eastern.